This program is sponsored by an education
grant provided by the Pfizer Corporation.

7
00:00:33,240 --> 00:00:38,068
The objective of this three hour program
is to integrate national patient safety

8
00:00:38,068 --> 00:00:42,967
goals, requirements in clinical practice
in areas of patient identification,

9
00:00:42,967 --> 00:00:48,400
Universal Protocol, medication labeling,
